- Attack!
- Come on!

34
00:02:56,200 --> 00:03:02,000
And now a toast to Gunma
and his debut in Formula 3!

35
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:05,989
- Cheers!
- Thank you, my friends!

36
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:16,988
I still can't believe that
you'll be entering Formula 3!

37
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:19,111
I thought it would
take at least six months ...

38
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:21,031
...for you to make it.

39
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:24,317
- It's all about skill and talent!
- You are a genius!

40
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:27,751
Well, soon enough
you'll all see what I'm made of.

41
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:31,236
After I win the races in
Formula 3 I'll head to Formula 1.

42
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:34,153
Monaco, Brazil ... All the
grand prizes will be mine!

43
